    "When there were considerable differences among raters, the committee displayed the paper and decided the final mark in cooperation.",
    "It is worth mentioning that the grading rubric included sub-categories about the overall organization, coherence, word choice, and use of conventions appropriately after examining the TOEFL and IELTS writing rubrics.",
